程序包 com.github.nickvl.xspring.core.log.aop.annotation

  • 枚举概要 
    枚举 说明
    LogPoint
    Parts of the method to be logged.
  • 注释类型概要 
    注释类型 说明
    LogDebug
    Annotation indicating that a method (or all methods on a class) should be logged.
    LogError
    Annotation indicating that a method (or all methods on a class) should be logged.
    LogException
    Annotation for logging specified exceptions thrown from a method (or all methods on a class).
    LogException.Exc
    Holds description exceptions to log.
    LogFatal
    Annotation indicating that a method (or all methods on a class) should be logged.
    Logging
    Meta annotation that indicates a log method annotation.
    LogInfo
    Annotation indicating that a method (or all methods on a class) should be logged.
    LogTrace
    Annotation indicating that a method (or all methods on a class) should be logged.
    LogWarn
    Annotation indicating that a method (or all methods on a class) should be logged.
    Lp
    An annotation to mark arguments of the method to be logged.
